Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Reagan faces reality
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wtlb
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 24 Jan 1982
President Reagan scores lowest ever popularity rating as he prepares for his first State of the Union address. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less